  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Phase II randomized study for the comparison of the Gemcitabine plus Docetaxel and the
      Ifosfamide treatment of patients with relapsed osteosarcoma
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patients with relapsed osteosarcoma will be randomized to receive Gemcitabine plus Docetaxel
      or High Doses Ifosfamide (continuous infusion) every 3 weeks, up to 6 weeks
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
